trans-unit.source: Provides design-time visual support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Gir utformingen visual støtte for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The WebZoneDesigner class is the abstract base class for both <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner>, which all the other zone designers inherit from.
trans-unit.target: WebZoneDesigner klassen er abstrakt basisklasse for begge <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner>, der alle andre zone-utviklere arve fra.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner>

trans-unit.source: By inheriting directly from <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> instead of <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner>, it allows implementations of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method that do not automatically clear the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A> collection, thus enabling the designer to render exceptions from child controls.
trans-unit.target: Ved arving direkte fra <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>i stedet for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner>, den tillater implementeringer av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>metode som ikke automatisk fjerner den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A>samling, slik at designer til å gjengi unntak fra underordnede kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Like other designers in this namespace, WebZoneDesigner overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebZoneDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property to always return `true`.
trans-unit.target: Som andre utviklere i dette navneområdet WebZoneDesigner overstyrer den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebZoneDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>til å returnere alltid `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebZoneDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the designer bound to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en forekomst av designer bundet til det tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone"></xref> control associated with the designer.
Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om designer må bruke en midlertidig kopi i stedet for den faktiske kontrollen som er forbundet med designer til å generere utformingen markup.
